Question: Many universities require that freshman live on campus dorm during the first year of college. In your opinion, is this a good or a bad thing? Explain your opinion on this issue.
Answer:
i think that this is a great thing. forcing students to live on campus their first year forces them to integrate into their schools social sphere. i know i made tons of friends just from living in my freshman hall alone. plus when you live on campus you spend more time in the genersl social spaces instead of having to walk or drive back home a good distance.